"                                        'domain': 'example.com',\n"
"                                        'path': '/currency'}])"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../topics/request-response.rst:78
msgid ""
"The latter form allows for customizing the ``domain`` and ``path`` "
"attributes of the cookie. This is only useful if the cookies are saved for "
"later requests."
